      Create `src/client/shared/Spaarke.DocumentOperations/src/hooks/useDocumentActions.ts` as a verbatim copy. Update relative imports as needed (auth client, fetch helpers, types). If the hook depends on SemanticSearch-internal types, move those types to the shared lib too (only the strictly-required ones).
    </step>
    <step order="3" name="Export from barrel">
