    <step order="6" name="Run existing SemanticSearch tests">
      Run SemanticSearch's existing test suite and confirm no regressions. If a test imports the hook by deep path, note for task 033 fix-up.
    </step>
    <step order="7" name="Run code-review + adr-check (FULL rigor)">
      Per root CLAUDE.md §8, FULL rigor for code-move tasks. Invoke code-review and adr-check skills at Step 9.5.
    </step>
    <step order="8" name="Update TASK-INDEX">
      Update `projects/spaarkeai-compose-r1/tasks/TASK-INDEX.md` status for task 031 to ✅.
    </step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
